 Rules and Guidelines: 


    1. Applicants MUST respond to all the questions pertaining to that
    post.
    2. All applicants are strongly advised to meet and discuss their
    candidature and their ideas/new initiatives with all the captains and
    core members of SOC team.
    3. A scanned copy of the latest grade card should be attached along
    with the completed application. Workflow screen shots are also acceptable.
    4. The applications have to be mailed in PDF format with the subject
    as "<CMSIF_<your name_<roll number".

